name: A BW Journal by Donna Martinez

metadata.name: Silo Trio in BW
metadata.description:
On the rural plains of eastern Colorado, it is hard to not find, Silos.  Farmers fill them with grain, like wheat and corn at harvest to be delivered.  These are made of aluminum and feature many beautiful lines.  They make great BW images. Thank you for enjoying.
Nikon Z7
28-300mm 3.5 Nikkor
8065x5377 pixels at 300DPI
1/640 at f8 ISO80
